components.name: Extract Vendor Shipment CSVs
components.description: Reads raw shipment CSV files from three vendors and passes the data via XCom for downstream processing.

upstream_policy.description: Root extraction task, no upstream dependencies.

components.name: Cleanse and Normalize Shipment Data
components.description: Combines vendor datasets, normalizes SKU formats, validates dates, filters invalid records, and enriches with location reference data.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after all three vendor extraction tasks have completed successfully.

components.name: Load Cleansed Shipments to Inventory Database
components.description: Writes the cleansed shipment records into the inventory_shipments table in PostgreSQL.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after the cleansing and normalization step completes successfully.

components.name: Send ETL Summary Email
components.description: Sends a daily email summary to the supply chain team after successful database load.

upstream_policy.description: Triggered only after the database load completes successfully.

connections.purpose: SMTP server for sending notifications to supply-chain-team@company.com

description.description: Three-stage ETL pipeline for supply chain shipment data processing with parallel extraction, transformation, and loading, scheduled daily.
